OL,3,CBill Nighy says starring in IVF film
OL,4,Cwas 'very special'
OL,6,F"You can't get a bigger story than
OL,7,Fthis": Bill Nighy talks about his new
OL,8,Ffilm, Joy.
OL,10,FActor Bill Nighy says starring in his
OL,11,Fupcoming film, which tells the
OL,12,Fremarkable true story of the world's
OL,13,Ffirst IVF baby, was "very special".
OL,15,FJoy focuses on the birth of Louise Joy
OL,16,FBrown, the first "test-tube baby" born
OL,17,Fin Oldham General Hospital in 1978,
OL,18,Fand the tireless 10-year journey to
OL,19,Fmake it possible.
