OL,3,CBill Nighy says starring in IVF film
OL,4,Cwas 'very special'
OL,6,FNighy plays scientist Patrick Steptoe,
OL,7,Fwho created the technology, which is
OL,8,Fused to treat infertility, alongside
OL,9,Fnurse Jean Purdy and physiologist Sir
OL,10,FRobert Edwards.
OL,12,FSpeaking about his role in the film at
OL,13,Fpremiere in London, the actor said:
OL,14,F"It's very special. It's such a big
OL,15,Fstory.
OL,17,F"You can't get a bigger story given
OL,18,Fthat now 16 million women have
OL,19,Fchildren who wouldn't have had
OL,20,Fchildren if these three obsessives had
OL,21,Fnot persevered.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
