OL,3,CBill Nighy says starring in IVF film
OL,4,Cwas 'very special'
OL,6,F"Over a 10-year period they failed and
OL,7,Ffailed and failed, attacked by the
OL,8,Fnewspapers, the church, their
OL,9,Ffamilies, and the medical association
OL,10,F- no one supported them.
OL,12,F"They had no funding. They did it out
OL,13,Fof temporary buildings out the back of
OL,14,FOldham hospital because nobody in
OL,15,FLondon would touch them.
OL,17,F"But they persevered. Louise Brown was
OL,18,Fborn 47 years ago and everybody shut
OL,19,Fup."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
