OL,3,CBill Nighy says starring in IVF film
OL,4,Cwas 'very special'
OL,6,FNighy, 74, best known for Love
OL,7,FActually and the Pirates of the
OL,8,FCaribbean franchise, said the subject
OL,9,Fof the film was close to the heart of
OL,10,Feveryone involved.
OL,12,FHe said: "The producer has an IVF
OL,13,Ffamily, the director has an IVF
OL,14,Ffamily, and the writer has IVF
OL,15,Fchildren, so there was that element
OL,16,Fwhich informed the atmosphere to some
OL,17,Fdegree."
