OL,3,CBill Nighy says starring in IVF film
OL,4,Cwas 'very special'
OL,6,FThe film shines a light on Jean Purdy,
OL,7,Fthe female scientist whose involvement
OL,8,Fin the story was "airbrushed out of
OL,9,Fthe whole affair because she didn't
OL,10,Fhave a penis", Nighy said.
OL,12,F"One of the millions of occasions
OL,13,Fwhere women have been dismissed as
OL,14,Fpart of the story, because they were
OL,15,Fconsidered sub-humans."
OL,17,FLouise Brown, 46, was present at the
OL,18,Fpremiere and said it was "surreal but
OL,19,Famazing" that the film about her life
OL,20,Fwas giving the creators of IVF the
OL,21,F"recognition that they deserve".
