OL,3,CBill Nighy says starring in IVF film
OL,4,Cwas 'very special'
OL,6,FShe said: "It's very surreal but
OL,7,Famazing that the three pioneers (of
OL,8,FIVF) are finally getting the
OL,9,Frecognition that they deserve.
OL,11,F"It wasn't easy for them, but they
OL,12,Fkept at it and thank you that they did
OL,13,Fbecause without them, me and 12
OL,14,Fmillion others wouldn't be here."
OL,16,FJoy will be released in the UK on 15
OL,17,FNovember and will arrive on Netflix on
OL,18,F22 November.
